        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Exposing Congressional Drug Abuse Act</b></p> <p>This concurrent resolution requires each Member of Congress, including a Delegate or Resident Commissioner, to submit to random tests for illegal use of controlled substances.</p>]]></text>
